###Creer un qcm
POST http://localhost:3001/qcms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "name": "Culture Numérique"
  }
}


###Récupère le résultat d'un QCM (score) |
POST http://localhost:3001/qcms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "name": "Culture Numérique"
  }
}

###Creer un qcm
POST http://localhost:3001/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiZW1haWwiOiJzYWJyaW5hLWxvZ2luQHRlc3QuZnIiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODAzOTM0ODAsImV4cCI6MTc4MDQwMDY4MH0.h1no01eg7Fibg6b0OtLVMOd_zGVHmu_1lELgUUvc4DY"

{
  "data": {
    "description": "Que signifie HTTP ?",
    "qcmId": 1
  }
}

###Soumettre une reponse
GET  http://localhost:3001/qcms/1/result
Content-Type: application/json

{
